name: #00033 Iris & Mummy 220120
description: #00033 Iris & Mummy 220120 was created 20th January 2022, This was a portrait of Iris and Mummy, the form of her figures are starting to develop into stick like figures but it is becoming clearer to see the features she is trying to capture in the faces and the long legs and feet. Iris has also signed off on this drawing with an "I" for good measure! This is NFT number 33 released by the Youngest Artist in the NFT World, Iris. Age at release - 3 years old.
